      <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c9"><span class="c10 c11 c15">Primer Caso. – </span><span class="c1">Para pacientes que primera vez se van a registrar sus datos.</span></p><p class="c9"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 453.00px; height: 149.79px;"><img alt="" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/BTZeJ9Q6KNeNzlEEdMd8i3gosiwYevDK2wgXniEc8DijEL8kxXLxwkteOtENvd0jIANtCsFGFCOUHtEEp5VVCaofVYBbGyojeUdh4JaNv8w12BCEu-PKKD9oI52gHErb_r1-QLU" style="width: 453.00px; height: 149.79px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
      <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c1"></span></p>
      <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c1"></span></p>
