                    <p class="c7"><span class="c2"></span></p><p class="c29"><span class="c5 c6">REGISTRAR HOSPITALIZACION DEL PACIENTE</span></p>
                    <ol class="c25 lst-kix_list_15-0 start" start="1"><li class="c36 c37 li-bullet-0"><span class="c2">Click en el botón ubicado en la parte superior derecha &nbsp;“Nuevo”. &nbsp;</span></li></ol>
                    <p class="c27"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 75.93px; height: 56.93px;"><img alt="" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/4MNcWtOBF-dcT5qV8OIf-R053PHEydf9WatZeKXG9kvJvHu6XTgXCjYH66Bj7fjJ37RDMVR4ONlXqCeVzvGjmRYKqi9fH3sDfKjJFdDSwHtZREhVFYXK689fh09kZ1hWvW3mKZU" style="width: 75.93px; height: 56.93px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p>
                    <p class="c7"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c36"><span class="c2">&nbsp; </span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 628.07px; height: 310.60px;"><img alt="" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/cnHP8PtSbeCWo86iznuDjshz0s2z2g_2go86wgN0TpAUlOzt3GuFOVAvRXPXxsWG1iLOxvrjEbzZZ78z6uq_A20pvZGaV2ncIY-UZ8RmQ-2G6unxETIpQPNhrthT1GjMOCXuoQ8" style="width: 628.07px; height: 310.60px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c7 c39"><span class="c2"></span></p><p class="c9 c13"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9"><span class="c5 c6">REALIZAR EL ALTA A PACIENTE</span></p>
                    <ol class="c25 lst-kix_list_8-0 start" start="1"><li class="c12 li-bullet-2"><span class="c2">Click en el Menú Hospitalización.</span></li>
                      <li class="c9 c21 li-bullet-3"><span class="c2">Click en Dar Alta.</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 623.87px; height: 183.80px;"><img alt="" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/mX3pDWa2xo94_Ay7kcS6KXWZ-u_MxpmHehoEtJwBvOs_pQyvXgUNlkgjOJybTg8ciaJnqZuey6QYxjjcl1SDPYjWlbjkrRsfzjpbt3VWR9IuCtwBp70pzwFe_9NI_kEzQJF2QvM" style="width: 623.87px; height: 183.80px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span>
                      </li>
                    </ol>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c2"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c5 c6"></span></p>
                    <p class="c9"><span class="c5 c6">DAR DE ALTA AL PACIENTE HOSPITALIZADO-</span></p>
                    <p class="c9 c13"><span class="c5 c6"></span></p>
                    <ol class="c25 lst-kix_list_9-0 start" start="1">
